{"title":"村野，从春到夏","authors":["杨松杰"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":7,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"村野，从春到夏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨松杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝴蝶的透明翅上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永无沉落的夕阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立春那天一声牛嘶传到今日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像民歌滚动在晶露中间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹲在门前吃饭的老翁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筷子敲打碗沿一声响过一声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农事爬满了眼角皱纹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是草帽出门的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰年景象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应验了春联上预兆的吉祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长篙和民谣同时滑动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗味开始弥漫落霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦粒在齿间和手掌上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被咬着被摊开被检验"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人和土地一见如故"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}